eElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>oncancel</strong></code>プロパティは<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a>のミックスイン(mixin)で、<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/cancel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">cancel</a></code>イベントを<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a>要素に送るための<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code>です</p>\n\n<p><code>cancel</code>イベントはユーザーが<code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code>を閉じる意向を示した際に発火します。このイベントハンドラーはイベントをバブリングから防ぎます。つまり、いかなる親ハンドラーであってもイベントは通知されません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>target</em>.oncancel = <em>functionRef</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>functionRef</code>は関数名もしくは<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\">関数式</a>です。この関数は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>オブジェクトを唯一の引数として受け取ります。</p>\n\n<p><code>oncancel</code>ハンドラーは一つのオブジェクトに対して一つのみ割り当てることが可能です。より柔軟であることから<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a>メソッドを代わりに使用するのも良いかもしれません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様書","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-oncancel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">oncancel の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/cancel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">cancel</a></code> イベント</li>\n <li>HTML <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a> 要素</li>\n <li>関連するイベントハンドラー: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close_event\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onclose</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"oncancelプロパティはGlobalEventHandlersのミックスイン(mixin)で、cancelイベントを<dialog>要素に送るためのevent handlerです","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/globaleventhandlers/oncancel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/globaleventhandlers/oncancel/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}